This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with semantic segmentation of road scenes. It also involves training neural networks, which makes it likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of adaptive training suggests that it may belong to the Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-category. Finally, the fact that the paper deals with road scenes suggests that it may also belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) sub-category.
